<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1906-05-08T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1906-05-08T00:00:00-05:00" n="99" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d99">
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Sorsby</persName> to
                                the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">La
                                        Paz</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-05-08"><hi rend="italic">May 8,
                                1906</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Government of Bolivia extends through the legation cordial invitation
                            Secretary of State to visit Bolivia during his southern trip. Bolivian
                            minister at Washington also has been instructed.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Sorsby.</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>